// Bind app.manifest as the executable's manifest resource.
// Resource id 1, type 24 (RT_MANIFEST). Without this, MinGW builds fall
// back to comctl32 v5 — controls render in the Windows 95 / Classic
// theme. The MSVC #pragma comment(linker, "/manifestdependency:...") in
// app.cpp accomplishes the same thing for MSVC builds, but MinGW ignores
// linker pragmas, so we need a real .rc file.
1 24 "app.manifest"
